  %% Diagram 60: Vendor Campaign Orchestration (Coupon and Flash Sale)

  Goal[Vendor chooses objective\nclear stock/boost conversion/festival push]
  Input[Select products and campaign window]
  Optimize[POST /api/ai/coupon-optimize]
  Suggest[Suggested discount + expected movement]

  PolicyGate{Discount within policy bounds?}
  Clamp[Clamp or reject out-of-policy discount]

  FlashCheck{Flash sale slot requested?}
  StockGate{Stock sufficient for slot cap?}
  Adjust[Adjust slot cap or reject schedule]

  Confirm[Vendor confirms campaign]
  Publish[Publish coupon/flash sale]
  Live[Campaign live with countdown]

  Goal --> Input --> Optimize --> Suggest --> PolicyGate
  PolicyGate -- No --> Clamp --> Suggest
  PolicyGate -- Yes --> FlashCheck

  FlashCheck -- No --> Confirm
  FlashCheck -- Yes --> StockGate
  StockGate -- No --> Adjust --> Input
  StockGate -- Yes --> Confirm

  Confirm --> Publish --> Live
